				\begin{document}$$a_{\exp}^{{\rm{Pio}} 10} = (7{.}84 \pm 0{.}01) \,\, \times \,\, {10^{- 10}}\,{\rm{m}}/{{\rm{s}}^{2}}{.}$$\end{document} Similarly, the experimental value for Pioneer 11 was found to be: 5.2\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
