Another possible on-board systematic error is from the expulsion of the He being created in the RTGs from the α-decay of 238Pu. According to the discussion presented in Section 4.4.2, Anderson et al. estimate the bias and error in acceleration due to He-outgassing as 5.19\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
