				\begin{document}$${g_{\mu \nu}} = {b_{\mu \nu}} + {h_{\mu \nu}},\quad {h_{\mu \nu}} \ll {b_{\mu \nu}},$$\end{document} and derives the linearized Einstein equations for hμν: 6.19\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
