				\begin{document}$${I_\varphi} = L,\quad {I_r} = - L + {{GmM} \over R}\sqrt {{m \over {2\vert E\vert}}},$$\end{document} which determine the energy, E, momentum, p and the eccentricity, e, of an orbit: 6.23\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
