As an upshot of these efforts, Bertolami et al. [50] explored a particular family of f(R) Lagrangians that gives rise to an extra acceleration in the form 6.26\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
